# Plugin Testing Reminder

⚠️ **IMPORTANT**: After making any changes to the plugin code, always run the test script to ensure everything is working:

```bash
nu test-minimal.nu
```

This script will:
1. Build the project (`dotnet build NuPluginDotNet.sln`)
2. Load the plugin (`plugin add ./bin/Debug/net8.0/win-x64/nu_plugin_dotnet.exe`)
3. Test basic functionality (`dn new "System.Object"`)


## Debug Mode:
If you encounter issues, enable debug logging:
```bash
$env:NU_PLUGIN_DOTNET_DEBUG="true"; nu test-minimal.nu
```

Always check the logs if the plugin fails.


**Remember**: Always test after code changes to catch issues early!
